<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿和狼宝宝们坐在圆圈里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他玩儿着一些在月光下闪闪发光的白卵石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸用鼻子轻轻地朝前推了推毛克利</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，大家快看！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉像对别的狼宝宝喊过那样喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还没等狼们来得及回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>岩石后面就传来了低吼声，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是谢尔坎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个宝宝是我的！”老虎低吼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把他给我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，大家快看！”阿克拉喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好好儿看看这个宝宝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>森林法则是要有两只狼为狼宝宝说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是狼群接受狼宝宝的方式。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁想为这个宝宝说话？”阿克拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈很紧张，准备要保护毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉还在等待狼说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了狼群里的狼，只有一个动物允许参加狼群的岩石会议。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就是巴鲁，一头懒洋洋的棕熊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他教狼宝宝们森林法则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁只吃坚果、树根和蜂蜜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，森林里的动物们都不怕他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎越走越近，棕熊抬起前爪站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大声咕哝：“我为这个人类宝宝说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让他跟着狼群跑吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会像教其他宝宝一样教他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有谁想为这个人类宝宝说话？”阿克拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，一个黑影跳进了圆圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是巴希拉，一只黑豹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼们马上向后退。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿克拉，我没资格呆在这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑豹的嗓音像树上掉下的蜂蜜那样温柔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，森林法则说一个宝宝的生命可以被买下来，对吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”几只年轻的狼急切地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>年轻的狼们总是很饿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿克拉！”一只狼大喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听巴希拉的吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个宝宝可以收钱卖掉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是森林法则。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑豹温柔地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想提议一个买卖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁已经替这个小男孩儿说话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你们其他人接受他，我就分给你们一些好吃的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是一头肥牛，刚杀的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈看着狼爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只黑豹为什么替毛克利说话？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他狼聚到一起商量这个情况。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个小男孩儿会在冬天下雨时死掉的。”一只狼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他会被太阳晒死的。”另一只狼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个宝宝能把我们怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“答应了吧，让他和狼群一起跑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，狼们同意接受毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利安静地坐着，玩儿着那些白卵石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当狼们看着毛克利时，阿克拉高喊道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼们！大家快看，大家快看！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，狼群就开始下山去吃黑豹许诺的美餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉、巴希拉、巴鲁和毛克利一家子留在山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎发出可怕的咆哮声，大步离开了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想怎么咆哮就怎么咆哮吧，老虎。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉嘟囔道，“我感觉总有一天，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个人类宝宝毛克利，会让你因为另一个原因咆哮的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉笑着转头看狼妈妈和狼爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类非常有智慧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许你们的人类宝宝能在某些方面帮助我们狼群。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利的父母点头表示感谢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，狼爸爸转过头对熊说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您今天帮忙，巴鲁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请尽快开始训练毛克利吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他得学习如何成为一只狼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>